                  <p> This privacy policy ("Policy") applies to the Website located at www.Blabeey.com (the "Site") owned and operated by Blabeey, Inc. ("Blabeey" "we" or "us") and the Blabeey service accessed through our mobile application (the "service" or "app").  The Blabeey Site and app are owned and operated by Blabeey Inc., located at 387 Magnolia Ave, Suite 103-233, Corona, California, United States.</p>
