                  <!-- Terms desc -->
                  <p>Blabeey and its partners may use cookies or similar technologies to analyze trends, administer the website, track users' movements around the website, and to gather demographic information about our user base as a whole. You can control the use of cookies at the individual browser level, but if you choose to disable cookies, it may limit your use of certain features or functions on our website or service.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- Terms desc ends -->
                <div class="clearfix"></div>
